# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  ⛔ MAINNET — AUDIT-GATED, NOT DEPLOYED. Real funds. Leave BLANK until audited.  ⛔
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  This repo is TESTNET-ONLY today and UNAUDITED — there is NO mainnet deployment
#  and NO mainnet claim. Every key below exists ONLY so each chain has a mainnet
#  PROFILE next to its testnet one (config/readiness). Each is # CONFIRM / OWNER-FILL
#  and # AUDIT-GATED: do NOT fill or run `make deploy-<chain>-mainnet` until a
#  third-party security audit is complete (the Makefile mainnet targets are gated
#  behind MAINNET_AUDITED=yes). As on testnet, every token/feed address resolves to
#  address(0) when blank ⇒ DeployAll SKIPS it; a guessed real mainnet address is
#  forbidden (law #4 — it would imply a deployment we have not made). Fill the
#  _PLATFORM_TREASURY only when you actually broadcast that chain (required then).

