# eip155-5042.json (shortName "arc-mainnet", native USDC) → the likely id is 5042, but that
# entry has EMPTY rpc/explorer and Arc is still public testnet ("mainnet beta, summer 2026").
# Leave this BLANK until Circle ships a live mainnet RPC; then set ARC_MAINNET_CHAIN_ID=5042
# (confirm against the registry once its rpc[]/explorers[] populate). Testnet id 5042002 is live.
